              <h2 className="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-6 md:mb-8 tracking-tight text-center lg:text-left">Personalized Growth Report</h2>
              <p className="text-slate-600 text-lg md:text-xl mb-10 md:mb-12 leading-relaxed text-center lg:text-left">Adjust these numbers to see the exact time and revenue savings for your practice.</p>

              <div className="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8">
                <div className="bg-slate-50 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-[1.5rem] md:rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 focus-within:ring-4 focus-within:ring-blue-100 transition-all">
